# ============================================================
# Optional: allow selected curated PNG/JPG assets
# ============================================================
# These are NOT ignored:
# data/characters/*.png
# data/episodes/*/keyframes/selected/*.png
#
# Keep only final selected lightweight reference images in Git.
# Do not commit random generated variants.


